@startuml checkbox-page-process-flow
participant "User" as User
participant "Checkbox Page" as CheckboxPage
participant "Vuex Store" as Vuex
participant "API Server" as Server
participant "Router" as Router

User -> CheckboxPage : Opens Checkbox Page
CheckboxPage -> Vuex : Checks if persisted sections exist

alt Sections exist in Vuex
    CheckboxPage -> Vuex : Load persisted sections data
else No persisted sections
    CheckboxPage -> Server : Fetch and parse template sections
    Server --> CheckboxPage : Receive parsed sections
    CheckboxPage -> Vuex : Store parsed sections
end

User -> CheckboxPage : Toggles checkboxes
CheckboxPage -> Vuex : Updates section check status

User -> CheckboxPage : Clicks "Start Processing"

CheckboxPage -> Vuex : Collects section data
CheckboxPage -> Vuex : Collects input, dropdown, and date field data

CheckboxPage -> Router : Redirects to Processing Page
@enduml
